│   SajakVisual - SaaS Digital Invitation          │
│   Developed by: Muhamad Faidil Aziz              │
│   © 2026 SajakVisual. All rights reserved.       │
│   System is running smoothly...                  │
│                                                  │
╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
`);
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
